<div id="Idea_2522"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2522-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2522">Civil Liberty Protection Act&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/0-4049">alarmlv</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">10 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Any bill introduced which has the potential to impact civil liberties in any way, must be introduced as a stand-alone bill who's name reflects the true nature of the bill, in a language that instantly and clearly identifies its content, and cannot be combined with, or hidden within, any other bill or group of bills.</div>
