<div id="Idea_2496"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2496-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2496">Get rid of Presidential Signing Statements as line-item vetoes&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/0-4049">kirsten.mcneil</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">10 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">The Executive Branch needs to accept that they operate under the laws passed by Congress, and stop using signing statements to negate part of these laws. If part of a law is unconstitutional, it should be reviewed by the Judiciary. The Executive has the responsibility to faithfully execute the laws passed by the popular body, and is not above such limitations on power. Even though these statements are published in the Federal Register, they represent a sneaky action by the Executive and degrade trust.</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_2496" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_2496', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2237&topicID=2496')">Comments (3)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_2496"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2237">Making Government Operations More Open</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=signing statement">signing statement</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_2496"></div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr id="row_2481">
<td width="120" align="center" valign="top" style="padding-left:10px;">
<div id="DiscussionTopicVote_2481">
<div id="IdeaScale_Vote" align="center"><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2481', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2237&topicID=2481&vote=1')"><img alt="Vote Up" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_up.gif"/>&nbsp;Looks Promising!</a></div><div style="padding:5px;font-size:2em"><a onmouseout="setTimeout('Bubble.hide()', 500)" onmouseover="Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 10 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 113</div><div>Votes Against : 18</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2481'))" style="text-decoration:none;" id="TopicVote_2481" href="javascript:Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 10 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 113</div><div>Votes Against : 18</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2481'))">95</a></div><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2481', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2237&topicID=2481&vote=-1')"><img alt="Vote Down" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_down.gif"/>&nbsp;I'm Not So Sure...</a></div></div>
